nodes.text: Buboicullaar, or Bubo for short, was a male frog-dog that was kept in Jabba's Palace by Jabba the Hutt. He was often looked over as being unintelligent, but was surprisingly smarter than many of Jabba's thugs. He once ate a detonation link needed for a bomb, foiling an attempt to assassinate Jabba. Ree-Yees, a Gran, had the task of looking after the creature.
